text: Pablo Rosenkjer was an alpine skier from Argentina. Rosenkjer competed at the 1948 Winter Olympics and the 1952 Winter Olympics. He was born on 8 September 1930 and died on 7 February 2020.Pablo Rosenkjer == References == Category:1930 births Category:2020 deaths Category:Skiers Category:Olympians for Argentina
